<html>
<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
bash : attempts to knock a foe off their feet<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
This skill is dexterity and weight dependant.  If successful your victim<br>
is knocked flying disturbing any spell they are casting.  It does minimal<br>
damage but is very valuable vs spell-casters.  Remember, if a mob is<br>
bigger than you, it gets much tougher to knock them over.<br>
</html>
</body>
